# Legacy Rails Standards

Follow the canonical standard: **`.ai/standards/legacy-rails.md`**

Key rules:
- Understand before you touch — reverse-document models, routes, jobs, integrations
- Characterize current behavior with tests before refactoring
- Strangler fig over big-bang rewrite; keep a documented rollback
- Upgrade Rails one minor at a time, never skipping majors

